OL,3,C'Masking is exhausting': MP calls for
OL,4,Cbetter support for neurodivergent
OL,5,Cworkers
OL,7,FAn MP who was diagnosed with ADHD as
OL,8,Fan adult has led a debate in
OL,9,Fparliament calling for improved
OL,10,Fsupport for neurodivergent people in
OL,11,Fthe workplace.
OL,13,FSarah Hall, who represents Warrington
OL,14,FSouth, says that while neurodiversity
OL,15,Faffects millions of employees across
OL,16,Fevery sector, "it is still too often
OL,17,Fmisunderstood, overlooked, or treated
OL,18,Fas a marginal issue".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
