OL,3,C'Masking is exhausting': MP calls for
OL,4,Cbetter support for neurodivergent
OL,5,Cworkers
OL,7,FSpeaking in Westminster Hall, the
OL,8,FLabour MP shared the story of her own
OL,9,Fdiagnosis, and the moving stories
OL,10,Fconstituents have shared about their
OL,11,Fexperiences.
OL,13,F"Like many people diagnosed later in
OL,14,Flife, that diagnosis didn't change who
OL,15,FI am, but it clarified things," she
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
