OL,3,C'Masking is exhausting': MP calls for
OL,4,Cbetter support for neurodivergent
OL,5,Cworkers
OL,7,F"It helped me understand why some
OL,8,Fenvironments drained me, why others
OL,9,Fenergised me, and why I had spent
OL,10,Fyears adapting myself to systems that
OL,11,Fwere never designed with people like
OL,12,Fme in mind."
OL,14,F"Since becoming a Member of
OL,15,FParliament, I've had many constituents
OL,16,Fwrite to me with experiences that echo
OL,17,Fthat same story. People who have spent
OL,18,Fyears masking.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
