OL,3,C'Masking is exhausting': MP calls for
OL,4,Cbetter support for neurodivergent
OL,5,Cworkers
OL,7,F"People who have been labelled
OL,8,Fdifficult or unreliable. People who
OL,9,Fhave quietly left jobs they were good
OL,10,Fat because the barriers became too
OL,11,Fmuch."
OL,13,FAround one in seven people in the UK
OL,14,Fare neurodivergent, including autistic
OL,15,Fpeople, people with ADHD, dyslexia,
OL,16,Fdyspraxia and other conditions.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
