OL,3,C'Masking is exhausting': MP calls for
OL,4,Cbetter support for neurodivergent
OL,5,Cworkers
OL,7,FMany qualify as disabled under the
OL,8,FEquality Act 2010, which means they
OL,9,Fare legally entitled to reasonable
OL,10,Fadjustments at work, but with long
OL,11,Fwaiting lists for formal diagnoses,
OL,12,Fnot everyone will have the paperwork
OL,13,Fto make sure their needs are being met.
OL,15,F"Many neurodivergent people hide parts
OL,16,Fof who they are at work to fit in,"
OL,17,FSarah said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
