OL,3,C'Masking is exhausting': MP calls for
OL,4,Cbetter support for neurodivergent
OL,5,Cworkers
OL,7,F"Sometimes they don't even realise
OL,8,Fthey're doing it. But masking is
OL,9,Fexhausting. It contributes to anxiety,
OL,10,Fisolation, burnout, and poor mental
OL,11,Fhealth.
OL,13,F"I recognise that experience myself.
OL,14,FAnd I know from constituents how
OL,15,Fcommon it is. People might not need to
OL,16,Fmask so much if workplaces were
OL,17,Fdesigned with difference in mind."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
