OL,3,C'Masking is exhausting': MP calls for
OL,4,Cbetter support for neurodivergent
OL,5,Cworkers
OL,7,FSarah is now calling for the
OL,8,FGovernment to make sure that people's
OL,9,Frights on paper are implemented in
OL,10,Fpractice, and to make sure that people
OL,11,Fcan access support based on need,
OL,12,Fregardless on whether they have yet
OL,13,Fhad a formal diagnosis of
OL,14,Fneurodivergence.
OL,16,FShe would also like to see
OL,17,Fneuroinclusive standards adopted in
OL,18,Fthe public sector, so it can be an
OL,19,Fexample for removing barriers people
OL,20,Fcan face when trying to carry out
OL,21,Ftheir work.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
