OL,3,C'Masking is exhausting': MP calls for
OL,4,Cbetter support for neurodivergent
OL,5,Cworkers
OL,7,FIn response, an Employment Minister
OL,8,Ftold the debate: "the right support
OL,9,Fmakes a huge difference, whether in
OL,10,Feducation or the workplace.
OL,12,F"It is important that good practice
OL,13,Fbecomes standard practice`not only
OL,14,Fdoes everyone deserve the chance to
OL,15,Ffulfil their potential, but a more
OL,16,Finclusive labour market is a stronger
OL,17,Flabour market."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
