OL,3,C'Masking is exhausting': MP calls for
OL,4,Cbetter support for neurodivergent
OL,5,Cworkers
OL,7,FDame Diana Johnson added that she will
OL,8,Fbe meeting with an independent panel
OL,9,Fwith expertise and lived experience of
OL,10,Fneurodiversity, to consider why
OL,11,Fneurodivergent people can have poor
OL,12,Fexperiences in work and a low overall
OL,13,Femployment rate.
OL,15,F"I am keen to show that this
OL,16,FGovernment are taking action," she
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,19,F"We hear what people are saying about
OL,20,Fthe need to address the particular
OL,21,Fconcerns of neurodivergent people."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
